Overall, as the DKPs are awared for things that require a guild to do them, it seems to all work out nicely but there are some ineffeciencies in the system and it seems they should be addressed.  (ie if the GM is giving out arbitrary IDKPS it seems that he should be able to say:  ok this no drop item is going to decay &quot;choose&quot; from the set of people or randomly assign who should loot it when it would clearly help them out.  ie with the inflationary economy giving the bread crumbs out for free really should not hurt the system.)<br>
